---
title: Pear and Blue Cheese Salad
source: Mom
tags: salad
servings: 6
---

In a small bowl, combine @oil{1/2%cup}, @blue cheese{1/2%cup}, @balsamic or cider vinegar{3%tbsp}, @salt{1%tsp}, and @large shallot{1} (minced). Set aside.

Before serving, combine @watercress{1%bunch} (stems removed), @Boston lettuce{2%heads} (torn into pieces), and @ripe pears{2} (peeled and sliced). Allow to marinate in dressing for about ~{15%minutes}. Add @peppered pecans{3/4%cup} and serve.
